// Unit 8: Fractions
_mergeUnitData(7, {"lessons":[{"points":["A fraction shows PART of a whole","The whole must be split into EQUAL parts","NUMERATOR (top) = parts you have","DENOMINATOR (bottom) = total equal parts","Parts MUST be equal size!"],"examples":[{"c":"#8e44ad","tag":"Fraction Parts","p":"The fraction 1/4 means:","s":"<div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin:10px 0\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 8px\"><svg width=\"100\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"#f3eaf8\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50.00,10.00 A40,40,0,0,1,90.00,50.00 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.00\" y2=\"10.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"90.00\" y2=\"50.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.00\" y2=\"90.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"10.00\" y2=\"50.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"50\" y=\"96\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#555\" font-weight=\"bold\">1/4</text></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#8e44ad;margin-top:4px\">1 out of 4 equal parts</div></div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:#555;margin:6px 0\"><svg width=\"36\" height=\"52\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 52\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><text x=\"18\" y=\"18\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" font-weight=\"bold\">1</text><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"27\" x2=\"32\" y2=\"27\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"18\" y=\"46\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" font-weight=\"bold\">4</text></svg>&nbsp;&nbsp;Top = parts you have &nbsp;|&nbsp; Bottom = total equal parts</div>","a":"1 out of 4 equal parts ✅"},{"c":"#8e44ad","tag":"Equal Parts","p":"Important rule:","s":"<div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin:10px 0\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 8px\"><svg width=\"100\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"#f3eaf8\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50.00,10.00 A40,40,0,0,1,50.00,90.00 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.00\" y2=\"10.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.00\" y2=\"90.00\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"50\" y=\"96\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#555\" font-weight=\"bold\">EQUAL</text></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#27ae60;margin-top:4px\">EQUAL - same size halves</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 8px\"><svg width=\"100\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"#f3eaf8\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L65.00,12.92 A40,40,0,0,1,65.00,87.08 Z\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"65\" y1=\"12.9\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"87.1\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#e74c3c;margin-top:4px\">NOT EQUAL - uneven split</div></div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:#555;margin:4px\">Both parts must be the <b>SAME SIZE</b>!</div>","a":"Parts must always be equal! ✅"},{"c":"#8e44ad","tag":"Examples","p":"Fractions in real life:","s":"<div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin:10px 0\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 12px\"><svg width=\"130\" height=\"130\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"46\" fill=\"#F0B27A\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"38\" fill=\"#E74C3C\"/><ellipse cx=\"36\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"7\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"62\" cy=\"36\" rx=\"11\" ry=\"7\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"34\" cy=\"60\" rx=\"8\"  ry=\"9\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"63\" cy=\"60\" rx=\"9\"  ry=\"7\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"72\" rx=\"7\"  ry=\"6\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><circle cx=\"38\" cy=\"32\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"63\" cy=\"40\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"36\" cy=\"62\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"64\" cy=\"62\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"4\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"96\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"96\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50,4 A46,46,0,0,1,96,50 Z\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50,4 A46,46,0,0,1,96,50 Z\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"46\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#e74c3c;margin-top:4px\">1 slice = 1/4</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#777\">(1 of 4 equal slices)</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 12px\"><svg width=\"130\" height=\"90\" viewBox=\"0 0 120 80\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><rect x=\"5\"  y=\"8\"  width=\"110\" height=\"52\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#8E44AD\" stroke=\"#6C3483\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><rect x=\"7\"  y=\"10\" width=\"106\" height=\"4\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"/><rect x=\"7\"  y=\"53\" width=\"106\" height=\"4\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.1)\"/><rect x=\"10\" y=\"14\" width=\"100\" height=\"40\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#6E2F0A\"/><rect x=\"12\" y=\"16\" width=\"96\" height=\"8\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.12)\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"54\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"34\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#5D1E00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"34\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#5D1E00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"11\" y=\"15\" width=\"48\" height=\"38\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#F39C12\" opacity=\"0.5\"/><rect x=\"11\" y=\"15\" width=\"48\" height=\"38\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#E67E22\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"35\" y=\"38\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"white\" font-weight=\"bold\" opacity=\"0.9\">1/2</text><text x=\"85\" y=\"38\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#784212\" font-weight=\"bold\" opacity=\"0.6\">1/2</text></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#8e44ad;margin-top:4px\">1 half = 1/2</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#777\">(1 of 2 equal pieces)</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 12px\"><svg width=\"150\" height=\"110\" viewBox=\"0 0 140 100\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><rect x=\"4\"  y=\"10\" width=\"132\" height=\"72\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#6E2F0A\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><rect x=\"10\" y=\"15\" width=\"120\" height=\"62\" rx=\"5\" fill=\"#784212\"/><rect x=\"12\" y=\"17\" width=\"116\" height=\"10\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\"/><line x1=\"40\"  y1=\"15\" x2=\"40\"  y2=\"77\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"70\"  y1=\"15\" x2=\"70\"  y2=\"77\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"77\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"10\"  y1=\"46\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"25\"  cy=\"30\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"55\"  cy=\"25\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"85\"  cy=\"32\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"27\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"25\"  cy=\"62\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"55\"  cy=\"58\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"85\"  cy=\"63\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"60\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2C1503\"/><rect x=\"11\" y=\"16\" width=\"28\" height=\"29\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#F39C12\" opacity=\"0.55\"/><rect x=\"11\" y=\"16\" width=\"28\" height=\"29\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#E67E22\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#e67e22;margin-top:4px\">1 piece = 1/8</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#777\">(1 of 8 equal pieces)</div></div></div>","a":"Fractions are everywhere! ✅"}],"practice":[{"q":"Pizza cut into 4 equal pieces. You eat 1. What fraction?<svg width=\"110\" height=\"110\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"44\" fill=\"#F0B27A\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"36\" fill=\"#E74C3C\"/><ellipse cx=\"35\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"63\" cy=\"35\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"33\" cy=\"60\" rx=\"7\" ry=\"8\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"63\" cy=\"60\" rx=\"8\" ry=\"7\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"71\" rx=\"7\" ry=\"5\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><circle cx=\"38\" cy=\"32\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"63\" cy=\"40\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"36\" cy=\"63\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"64\" cy=\"63\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#922B21\" stroke=\"#7B241C\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50.0,6.0 A44,44,0,0,1,94.0,50.0 Z\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><path d=\"M50,50 L50.0,6.0 A44,44,0,0,1,94.0,50.0 Z\" fill=\"rgba(39,174,96,0.35)\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.0\" y2=\"6.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"94.0\" y2=\"50.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"50.0\" y2=\"94.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"6.0\" y2=\"50.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"44\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg>","a":"1/4","h":"1 piece out of 4 equal pieces = one fourth!","e":"🍕"},{"q":"The TOP number of a fraction is called?","a":"Numerator","h":"NUMERATOR is at the top! It tells how many parts you have.","e":"🔢"},{"q":"The BOTTOM number of a fraction is called?","a":"Denominator","h":"Denominator is DOWN at the bottom! Total equal parts.","e":"🔢"},{"q":"A pie is cut into 8 equal slices. You take 3. What fraction do you have?<svg width=\"90\" height=\"90\" viewBox=\"0 0 90 90\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"#F5CBA7\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"32\" fill=\"#E59866\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L45.0,7.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,18.1 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L71.9,18.1 A38,38,0,0,1,83.0,45.0 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L83.0,45.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,71.9 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"7.0\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"71.9\" y2=\"18.1\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"83.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"71.9\" y2=\"71.9\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"83.0\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"18.1\" y2=\"71.9\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"7.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"18.1\" y2=\"18.1\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg>","a":"3/8","h":"You took 3 out of 8 equal slices. That is three eighths!","e":"🥧"},{"q":"A chocolate bar is split into 4 equal pieces. You eat 1. What fraction is eaten?<svg width=\"180\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 180 50\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><rect x=\"15\" y=\"4\" width=\"150\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#6E2F0A\" stroke=\"#4A1C03\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"17.0\" y=\"7\" width=\"33.0\" height=\"30\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#F39C12\"/><rect x=\"17.0\" y=\"7\" width=\"33.0\" height=\"30\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#E67E22\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"52.0\" y=\"7\" width=\"33.0\" height=\"30\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#784212\"/><rect x=\"87.0\" y=\"7\" width=\"33.0\" height=\"30\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#784212\"/><rect x=\"122.0\" y=\"7\" width=\"33.0\" height=\"30\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#784212\"/></svg>","a":"1/4","h":"You ate 1 out of 4 equal pieces. That is one fourth!","e":"🍫"},{"q":"A rectangle is divided into 6 equal parts. 2 parts are colored. What fraction is colored?<svg width=\"190\" height=\"38\" viewBox=\"0 0 190 38\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><rect x=\"0.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"31.7\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"63.3\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#f0e6f8\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"95.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#f0e6f8\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"126.7\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#f0e6f8\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"158.3\" y=\"0\" width=\"31.7\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#f0e6f8\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>","a":"2/6","h":"2 colored out of 6 equal parts = two sixths!","e":"📐"},{"q":"A pizza is cut into 8 equal slices. 5 slices are eaten. What fraction is left?<svg width=\"90\" height=\"90\" viewBox=\"0 0 90 90\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"#F0B27A\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"31\" fill=\"#E74C3C\"/><ellipse cx=\"32\" cy=\"26\" rx=\"8\" ry=\"5\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"57\" cy=\"31\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"5\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"54\" rx=\"6\" ry=\"7\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"57\" cy=\"54\" rx=\"7\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><ellipse cx=\"45\" cy=\"64\" rx=\"6\" ry=\"4\" fill=\"#F9E79F\"/><circle cx=\"35\" cy=\"28\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#922B21\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"57\" cy=\"36\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#922B21\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"33\" cy=\"57\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#922B21\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><circle cx=\"58\" cy=\"57\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#922B21\" opacity=\"0.9\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L45.0,7.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,18.1 Z\" fill=\"rgba(39,174,96,0.4)\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L71.9,18.1 A38,38,0,0,1,83.0,45.0 Z\" fill=\"rgba(39,174,96,0.4)\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L83.0,45.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,71.9 Z\" fill=\"rgba(39,174,96,0.4)\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"7.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"71.9\" y2=\"18.1\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"83.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"71.9\" y2=\"71.9\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"83.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"18.1\" y2=\"71.9\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"7.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"18.1\" y2=\"18.1\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#D35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg>","a":"3/8","h":"8 slices total, 5 eaten, so 3 are left. 3 out of 8 = three eighths!","e":"🍕"},{"q":"A circle is divided into 4 equal parts. 4 parts are shaded. What fraction is shaded?<svg width=\"90\" height=\"90\" viewBox=\"0 0 90 90\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"#f3eaf8\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L45.0,7.0 A38,38,0,0,1,83.0,45.0 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L83.0,45.0 A38,38,0,0,1,45.0,83.0 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L45.0,83.0 A38,38,0,0,1,7.0,45.0 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L7.0,45.0 A38,38,0,0,1,45.0,7.0 Z\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"7.0\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"83.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"45.0\" y2=\"83.0\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/><line x1=\"45\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"7.0\" y2=\"45.0\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg>","a":"4/4 = 1 whole","h":"All 4 parts are shaded! 4/4 equals one whole.","e":"⭐"}],"qBank":[{"t":"Pizza cut into 4 equal slices. Eat 1. Fraction?<svg width=\"110\" height=\"110\" viewBox=\"0 0 10