es = 1/2","h":"4 out of 8 slices is the same as one half! 4/8 = 1/2.","e":"🍕"},{"q":"Which fraction is closer to a whole pizza: 3/4 or 3/8?<svg width=\"190\" height=\"38\" viewBox=\"0 0 190 38\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><rect x=\"0.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"47.5\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"47.5\" y=\"0\" width=\"47.5\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"95.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"47.5\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"142.5\" y=\"0\" width=\"47.5\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#f0e6f8\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>","a":"3/4 is closer to a whole","h":"3/4 means bigger pieces! 3 large pieces is closer to a full pizza than 3 tiny pieces.","e":"🍕"},{"q":"A ribbon is cut into 2 equal halves. How many halves make the whole ribbon?<svg width=\"190\" height=\"38\" viewBox=\"0 0 190 38\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><rect x=\"0.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"95.0\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"95.0\" y=\"0\" width=\"95.0\" height=\"38\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>","a":"2 halves","h":"2/2 = 1 whole. Both halves together make the whole ribbon!","e":"🎀"},{"q":"A pie is divided into 8 equal slices. Jada eats 1 slice. Tom eats 3 slices. What fraction is left?<svg width=\"90\" height=\"90\" viewBox=\"0 0 90 90\" style=\"display:block;margin:4px auto\"><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"38\" fill=\"#F5CBA7\" stroke=\"#D4AC0D\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"45\" r=\"32\" fill=\"#E59866\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L45.0,7.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,18.1 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L71.9,18.1 A38,38,0,0,1,83.0,45.0 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M45,45 L83.0,45.0 A38,38,0,0,1,71.9,71.9 Z\" fill=\"rgba(142,68,173,0.5)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-wi